Comment: 0,0:00:00.08,0:00:02.30,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}字幕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.08,0:00:02.30,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}- Hi, it's me, Tim Dodd, the everyday astronaut.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.08,0:00:02.30,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}- 嗨 是我 Tim Dodd 每日宇航员
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.30,0:00:06.03,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}SpaceX is trying some pretty, crazy things with their Starship rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.30,0:00:06.03,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}SpaceX正在用他们的Starship火箭尝试一些相当疯狂的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.45,0:00:08.33,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But perhaps there's nothing more crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.45,0:00:08.33,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但最疯狂的也许是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.35,0:00:15.28,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}than letting your nine meter wide, 50 meter tall rocket fall out of the sky, belly first.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.35,0:00:15.28,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}让你的9米宽 50米高的火箭以机腹朝前的姿态从天而降
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.48,0:00:18.86,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And then try to light your engines basically very last moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.48,0:00:18.86,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}然后在最后一刻尝试点燃你的发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.06,0:00:23.18,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}in order to go from horizontal to vertical, to hopefully land softly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.06,0:00:23.18,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}以便从水平方向转为垂直方向 并希望可以软着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.41,0:00:27.93,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Now, the reason they're doing this is so they can make their terminal velocity as slow as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.41,0:00:27.93,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}现在 他们这样做的原因是 可以让终端速度尽可能地低
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.05,0:00:31.73,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}so the rocket engines don't have to do nearly as much work slowing the rocket down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.05,0:00:31.73,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样发动机不必做那么多工作来减缓火箭的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.86,0:00:34.80,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Now, in order to understand what exactly that all means,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.86,0:00:34.80,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么 为了理解这一切到底意味着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:37.78,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}there's a ton of physics lessons to unpack here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:37.78,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就需要学习大量的物理学课程
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.13,0:00:40.31,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And seeing all of these spectacular failures,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.13,0:00:40.31,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而在看到所有这些壮观的失败之后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.48,0:00:43.42,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}has brought up a lot of really good questions from you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.48,0:00:43.42,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们提出了很多真正的好问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:45.96,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But perhaps there's no bigger question than why.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:45.96,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但最大的问题也许是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.72,0:00:49.27,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Why are they doing that belly flop maneuver?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.72,0:00:49.27,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们为什么要做这种机腹向下的机动？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:52.99,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Why are they going from belly first and then flipping to tail down?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:52.99,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为什么他们要从机腹朝前 翻转到机尾朝下？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:55.70,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And why are they doing that maneuver so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:55.70,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而且他们为什么这么晚才做这个机动？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.02,0:00:59.04,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Why don't they just start that landing and maneuver just a little bit earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.02,0:00:59.04,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们为什么不早一点开始着陆和机动呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.04,0:01:03.05,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}to make sure there's enough time to make corrections, if something doesn't go right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.04,0:01:03.05,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样如果出问题了 还有足够的时间来纠正
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:04.06,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But we're also going to look at
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:04.06,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但我们也要看看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:09.51,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}what other options and constraints and variables SpaceX has with running on different number of engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:09.51,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}SpaceX使用不同数量发动机点火的情况有多少选择 限制和变量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.69,0:01:11.32,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Is running on more engines better?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.69,0:01:11.32,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}用更多的发动机点火是否更好？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.64,0:01:13.98,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Is starting that landing burn earlier better?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.64,0:01:13.98,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}更早开始着陆点火是否更好？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.25,0:01:17.23,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And can they use parachutes as a backup, if something goes wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.25,0:01:17.23,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}同时如果出现问题 他们能否使用降落伞作为备份？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:19.52,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And of course, we'll answer the ultimate question.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:19.52,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}当然 我们将回答一个终极问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:22.94,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Will this belly flop maneuver ever be safe enough for humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:22.94,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这种机腹向下的机动对载人来说是否足够安全？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.77,0:01:26.97,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I mean, could you even survive the G-forces of that crazy flip?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.77,0:01:26.97,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是指 你甚至能在这样疯狂翻转的过载力下生存吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.68,0:01:29.99,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Should SpaceX just scrap this whole idea
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.68,0:01:29.99,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}SpaceX是否应该放弃这整个想法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.04,0:01:34.96,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and go back to landing at more like a Falcon 9, which has proven to be highly successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.04,0:01:34.96,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}回到更像已被证明是非常成功的猎鹰9号的着陆方式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:39.50,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So today we're going to cover the wonders of terminal velocity, thrust to weight ratio,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:39.50,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因此 今天我们将讨论终端速度 推重比
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.50,0:01:41.38,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}gravity drag and engine throttling,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.50,0:01:41.38,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}重力拖拽和发动机节流
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:46.36,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}to see if we can figure out why SpaceX is pursuing such a crazy landing maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:46.36,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看看我们是否能弄清楚为什么SpaceX要追求如此疯狂的着陆机动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.85,0:01:51.34,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And if we even think that's a good idea or if maybe they should just go back to the drawing board.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.85,0:01:51.34,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}以及我们是否认为这是一个好主意 或者也许他们应该重新开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.99,0:01:52.70,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.99,0:01:52.70,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么让我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:54.73,1080P-sgbd-4s,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\blur4}- [Mission Control] Three, two, one,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:54.73,1080P-sgsm-6s,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\blur4}-  [任务控制]三 二 一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.73,0:01:55.73,1080P-sgbd-4s,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\blur4}and liftoff!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.73,0:01:55.73,1080P-sgsm-6s,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\blur4}起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.77,0:02:00.30,1080P-sgbd-4s,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\blur4}- [Neil] That's one small step for man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.77,0:02:00.30,1080P-sgsm-6s,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\blur4}-  [尼尔]这是对人类的一小步
