Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:06.95,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Now, right off the bat in case you haven't watched it already,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:06.95,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}现在 马上说下 如果你还没有看过的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:10.03,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}you might want to watch my complete guide to Starship,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:10.03,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你可能想看看我的{\i1}Starship完全指南{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.09,0:02:14.12,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}as we actually go over a lot of things that are going to be talked about in this video.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.09,0:02:14.12,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为我们实际上讨论了很多将在这个视频中谈到的事情
