Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:16.90,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以如果你没有看过 可能会有帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:21.28,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Or if you have other questions about Starship in general after you watched this video,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:21.28,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}或者如果你看了这个视频后对Starship有其他问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:24.49,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}give that one a watch, it'll likely help you find some answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:24.49,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看一下那段视频 它可能会帮助你找到一些答案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.71,0:02:29.30,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But the point of this video is to explain the physics behind the rocket science,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.71,0:02:29.30,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但这个视频的重点是解释火箭科学背后的物理学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:33.09,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}not to try and speculate but we're going to help you understand why.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:33.09,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而不是尝试和猜测 但我们要帮助你了解原因
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:37.84,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So when SpaceX does make changes, which they inevitably will,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:37.84,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么 当SpaceX确实不得不做出改变时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.91,0:02:41.66,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}you'll have some grasp on why they may have made those decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.91,0:02:41.66,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你就会对他们可能做出这些决定的原因有一些把握
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.73,0:02:43.08,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But this is a long video.
