Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:45.03,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}和我所有的长视频一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:48.10,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}we've got some timestamps for you guys for easy watching
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:48.10,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们已经为你们准备了一些时间戳 方便你们观看
